simple_inventory.py - execute a simple inventory command

This script creates a simple ROSpec (ID: 123) on the remote reader and
executes it in order to get a simple inventory tags.

To run the program use the command line:

 $ ./simple_inventory.py [<options>] host

where <options> are:
	-h - show this help message
	-d - enable debugging messages

and host is the internet address of the remote reader.
